{"tid":1562321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵:為鐵路運作安全著想，切勿在鐵路露天路段附近燃放孔明燈或攜帶金屬氣球進入港鐵範圍，以免影響鐵路運作","createTime":"2019-09-12T03:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T00:27:55.000Z","uid":72431,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a20e2566d8b42ce8c31327164e7047882f67d1ce","tid":1562321,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:26:52.000Z","msg":"港鐵指，與政府相關部門檢視近期情況，以及進行風險評估後，決定明天中秋節會按正常服務時間提供列車服務，將不會提供通宵列車服務，所有港鐵車站將按平常服務時間關閉，但因應預期上升的乘客量，部分港鐵路線將由下午三時起加密班次，一些較繁忙的車站將實施特別人流管理措施。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵呼籲市民在慶祝節日時，為鐵路運作安全著想，切勿在鐵路露天路段附近燃放孔明燈或攜帶金屬氣球進入港鐵範圍，以免影響鐵路運作，又指可浮起的LED氣球有燃燒及爆炸的潛在危險，乘客亦不可攜帶這類氣球進入港鐵範圍。"},{"pid":"622ea3994ae0a23444773f7f2af5ed20d5187a25","tid":1562321,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55621f1cacde17e64f4a28ba34c073ebadd31b25","tid":1562321,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:27:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"15518f024caeb74c8a8aa0cfa4ba3f45be2d72d0","tid":1562321,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:29:41.000Z","msg":"<strong>特登中秋節唔開通宵呀啦</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198b520e516ec05ec7d293bdd44272873c3da2b4","tid":1562321,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:32:48.000Z","msg":"港鐵宣布中秋夜將不提供通宵列車服務<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1562328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1562328</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e6dc3617581ccbe6b44e623446f1353ee95d2c44","tid":1562321,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363274f8228d0334434df2121b389089ae186589","tid":1562321,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4218a82bbc13d19edfa522c83f831b90d1a1cb6","tid":1562321,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:27:55.000Z","msg":"班冚家剷唔會因為你放嘢而停駛，到時夾硬行，有咩事又全部入你數<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機場就真係不宜放燈喇"}]}